den-to-ask-congress-for-unprecedented-14b-in-military-aid-for-israel/0000018b-4a84-d199-a7eb-dfde51e20000</guid></item><item><title>“俄罗斯轮盘赌”：以色列遭受轰炸最严重的城市的居民得不到保护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/russian-roulette-residents-of-israels-most-heavily-bombarded-city-are-left-unprotected/0000018b-49da-d03a-afcb-69fa722d0000</link><description>阿什凯隆是加沙战争中目标最严重的城市，该城的约 40,000 名居民缺乏适当的保护以免受火箭弹袭击——尽管事实上已经为此编列了资金预算</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 22:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/russian-roulette-residents-of-israels-most-heavily-bombarded-city-are-left-unprotected/0000018b-49da-d03a-afcb-69fa722d0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们在达兰萨拉冥想。突然，来自以色列的电话开始涌入”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-10-20/ty-article/.highlight/we-were-meditating-in-dharamshala-suddenly-phone-calls-from-israel-started-pouring-in/0000018b-49bc-d1fd-a59f-edbf900b0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：在战争期间，一名年轻女子返回以色列的家，而另一名年轻女子则在拉脱维亚与家人团聚</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 21:31:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-10-20/ty-article/.highlight/we-were-meditating-in-dharamshala-suddenly-phone-calls-from-israel-started-pouring-in/0000018b-49bc-d1fd-a59f-edbf900b0000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-49d3-d03a-afcb-69fb35f60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 21:27:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-49d3-d03a-afcb-69fb35f60000</guid></item><item><title>战时考验以色列的民主</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/testing-israels-democracy-in-wartime/0000018b-495e-d5d2-afef-cdffc47a0000</link><descrip